                     Klosterneunburg</rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place" ref="pl__sievering-immo_pfaffenberg_1">ain virtail weingarten, das nu zu
                        ainem stainpruch gemacht ist, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__sievering-pfaffenberg">gelegen am Phaffenperg pei
                           Obernsüfring</roleName>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__sievering-immo_pfaffenberg_2">zenagst
                              <add>an aim tail</add></roleName>
                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__sievering-immo_pfaffenberg_2"><roleName type="owner" corresp="org__wien">der stat</roleName> stainpruch, der
                           ettwenn auch ain weingarten und <roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__heinrich_heller_QGW_II_II_3480"><add>ettwenn</add>
                              <rs type="person" ref="pe__heinrich_heller_QGW_II_II_3480">Hainrichs
                                 Heller</rs></roleName> gewesen ist</rs>, an aim tail <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__sievering-immo_pfaffenberg_3">und an dem andern
                           zenagst</roleName>
                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__sievering-immo_pfaffenberg_3"><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__thomas_zimmermann_QGW_II_II_3480">seinem</roleName> weingarten, des auch ain virtail ist</rs>, <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3480_men_1"><rs type="fn" role="issuer">von <rs type="place" ref="pl__sievering-immo_pfaffenberg_1">dem</rs>
                              man</rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__klosterneuburg-augustiner_chorherren">nach
                                 Klosterneuburg</rs></rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><measure>einen halben Eimer
                                 Wein</measure>
                              <triggerstring n="fn">zu Bergrecht</triggerstring></rs> und <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><measure>einen Helbling</measure>
                              <triggerstring n="fn">zu Voitrecht</triggerstring></rs>
                           <triggerstring n="disp">dient</triggerstring></rs></rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II">um <measure>26 lb dn.</measure></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien">dem Bürgermeister
                        und Rathe der Stadt zu Wien</rs>.</rs></rs>
